<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.4">
<l>āycci mārkaḷu māyaru mañciṭap</l>
<l>pūtta nīḷkaṭam pēṟip pukappāyntu</l>
<l>vāytta kāḷiyaṉ mēṉaṭa māṭiya</l>
<l>kūtta ṉārvaril kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">the Dancer</l>
<l rend="indent">—who danced on the flourishing Kāliya</l>
<l rend="indent">after climbing up the tall, flowering Cadamba tree</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] sprang into the pond in order to enter [it]</l>
<l rend="indent">in such a way that the cowherdesses and the cowherds were scared</l>
<l>comes [to me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
